data.title: Bulla Cara Black Opaque
data.meta_description: Bulla Cara Loafer. Nodaleto luxury designer shoes. Loafers for women. Bulla block heels. International shipping. Free returns.
data.text:
Free Return : According to our Terms & Conditions, you have 14 days (counting after the reception of your package) to ask for a refund.

To ask for a return, please fill the form Request a return label. You can find the form inside the confirmation email or in the website footer.

A Nodaleto team member will get back to you with a return label. Once we receive your order back, we proceed with the refund. It may takes 3 opening days for the money to show on your bank account.

We are not able to process exchanges. If you wish to order a new size or a new color, please return your product for a refund and place a new order from the website.
